                    Order Now 
                    



Hide Details

Garden Fresh

            All your favorite veggies together on a delightfully delicious pizza.  Loaded with crisp green peppers, fresh-sliced onions, Crimini mushrooms, ripe black olives and vine-ripened Roma tomatoes. Lovingly prepared and delivered hot from our oven to your home.
            





Spinach Alfredo

            Spinach and a rich, creamy garlic Parmesan Alfredo sauce.
            




                    Order Now 
                    



Hide Details

Spinach Alfredo

            Delicious doesn’t have to be complicated. This irresistible pizza has a rich and creamy blend of spinach and garlic Parmesan Alfredo sauce topped with real cheese made from mozzarella.
            





Tuscan Six Cheese

            An authentic blend of Parmesan, Romano, Asiago, Fontina, Provolone and real cheese made from Mozzarella.
            




                    Order Now 
                    



Hide Details

Tuscan Six Cheese

            Experience the authentic taste of Italy! Layered with signature pizza sauce and an authentic blend of Parmesan, Romano, Asiago, Fontina, Provolone and real cheese made from Mozzarella. Baked hot and fresh then finished with Italian herb seasonings.
            




Papa's Lighter Choices





Mediterranean Veggie

            300 or fewer calories per slice with a lighter portion of cheese. Roma tomatoes, onions, banana peppers, mushrooms, ripe black olives and real cheese made from mozzarella.
            




                    Order Now 
                    



Hide Details

Mediterranean Veggie

            300 or fewer calories per slice with a lighter portion of cheese.
Love veggies? Our Mediterranean Veggie Pizza features fresh-sliced Roma tomatoes and onions, banana peppers, Crimini Mushrooms, ripe black olives and real cheese made from mozzarella, all on our signature pizza sauce and hand-tossed original crust.
            





Chicken and Veggie

            300 or fewer calories per slice with a lighter portion of cheese. Grilled chicken, onions, Roma tomatoes, green peppers, mushrooms, black olives and real cheese made from mozzarella.
            




                    Order Now 
                    



Hide Details

Chicken and Veggie

            300 or fewer calories per slice with a lighter portion of cheese. We trimmed the calories, not the taste. Grilled all-white chicken, fresh-sliced onions, Roma tomatoes and green peppers, plus Crimini mushrooms, ripe black olives and real cheese made from mozzarella, all layered on our signature pizza sauce and hand-tossed original crust.
            





Grilled Chicken and Canadian Bacon

            300 or fewer calories per slice with a lighter portion of cheese. Grilled chicken, Canadian bacon, Roma tomatoes and real cheese made from mozzarella.
            




                    Order Now 
                    



Hide Details

Grilled Chicken and Canadian Bacon

            300 or fewer calories per slice with slice with a lighter portion of cheese. Grilled all-white chicken, julienne-cut Canadian bacon, fresh-sliced Roma tomatoes and real cheese made from mozzarella, all layered on our signature pizza sauce and hand-tossed original crust.
            





Tropical Luau

            300 or fewer calories per slice with a lighter portion of cheese. Canadian bacon, sweet pineapple, green peppers and real cheese made from mozzarella.
            




                    Order Now 
                    



Hide Details

Tropical Luau

            300 or fewer calories per slice with a lighter portion of cheese. Our island-inspired pizza features julienne-cut Canadian bacon, sweet, juicy pineapple pieces, fresh-sliced green peppers and real cheese made from mozzarella, all layered on our signature pizza sauce and hand-tossed original crust.
            













