Rewards FAQs
Rewards Terms





Rewards FAQs
Rewards Terms

Close





Who can join Papa Rewards?

Any Papa John’s customer is eligible for participation in the Papa Rewards program. You must create an account with a valid email to enroll in the program.



How do I join Papa Rewards?

To enroll in Papa Rewards.

reate or sign into your papajohns.com account
If you have an account but haven't enrolled, click on Papa Rewards in the main navigation and check the box “Enroll me in Papa Rewards” and then Enroll.




How do I earn points?


Sign into your papajohns.com account
Earn 1 Papa Rewards Point for every $5 you spend online (including tax and delivery). Please note that Canadian customers earn 1 point for every $8 of online spend.
Points are awarded the next business day following your order completion
Qualifying purchases must be made via papajohns.com or through the digital apps




How do I redeem my points?


From the My Rewards page, view the available rewards you can redeem and click Redeem on the one you want
On the Confirmation Page, confirm promo code by clicking "Apply & Customize"
If required, in the Pizza Builder, begin customizing reward.




What is the Birthday Reward?

                            The Birthday Reward is an opportunity for Papa John’s to wish you a Happy Birthday during your birthday month with 10 bonus Papa Rewards points through a one-time use promo code you will receive via email. The Birthday Reward promo code and the accompanying bonus points expire on the last day of your birthday month. Once the points have been deposited, they are redeemable for a variety of menu items during your birthday month. This offer is valid at participating U.S. and Canadian restaurants only.
                            


When will I receive my Birthday Reward?

                            An email containing a unique promo code will be sent to you via email within the first week of your birthday month. If you enter the Birthday Reward promo code on a Papa John’s online ordering platform, Papa John’s will add 10 bonus Papa Rewards points to your Papa Rewards account. The unique code and bonus Papa Rewards points will expire on the last day of your birthday month.
                            


Is a papajohns.com account required to participate

                            Yes. You are required to have a papajohns.com account to use your Birthday Reward. You must also be a current Papa Rewards member by the first day of your birthday month and subscribed to receive email from Papa John’s.
                            


How do I use the unique birthday promo code?

                            To use the Birthday Reward, you must enter the unique promo code in the promo code box and select “Apply.” 10 bonus points will immediately be deposited in your Papa Rewards account. Your bonus points can be redeemed immediately or at a later date as long as it is used by the last day of your birthday month.
                            

Have more questions? Visit our FAQ Library





Registration & Eligibility

Any papajohns.com online customer can be eligible to enroll in the rewards program.
Account holders at papajohns.com also can register for the Papa John's Rewards program to earn rewards points. Registration and participation in the Papa John's Rewards program will only be available to customers purchasing online from www.papajohns.com from participating Papa John's restaurants.
After registration, and for the term of the Rewards program, your account may be credited with rewards points for online purchases made through papajohns.com from participating Papa John's restaurants. Accumulated points will be exchanged for product rewards or discounts for online purchases on papajohns.com from participating Papa John's restaurants. Papa John's International has the right to award products and discounts to shoppers based on their purchases and calculations based on Papa John's evaluation. The Papa John's Rewards program is offered only to shoppers who are 18 years of age or older. Membership awarding and redemption of rewards discount and other details will be the sole discretion of Papa John's. The Papa John's Rewards
program and its primary components including discounts, products and policies are decided and implemented at the sole discretion of Papa John's International. The above list is not exhaustive and can be modified by Papa John's as and when required without giving notice or any form of communication to Rewards program participants as individuals or groups.
No responsibility is assumed for any computer, telephone, cable, network, satellite, electronic or Internet hardware or software malfunctions, failures, connections, availability or garbled or jumbled transmissions, or service provider / Internet / web site / use net accessibility or availability, traffic congestion, or unauthorized human intervention. Though the above causes are not exhaustive and changes to the same can or will be made at the sole discretion of Papa John's as and when required without giving notice or any form of communication to Rewards program members as individuals or groups.



Duration of the Program & Account Termination

For each individual customer enrolled, rewards point accumulation begins with their first order made online at papajohns.com from participating Papa John's restaurants after registration. Papa John's International has the sole authority to dissolve the program at any time, any accumulated reward points, product rewards and discounts will no longer be active and entitlements to the program's existing members will cease to be available on and from that particular date. Papa John's is not liable to inform the Rewards program members of dissolution or closing the program in the event such situation arises.
We may terminate your access or suspend your eligibility for the Rewards program and its benefits or terminate your right of access to all or part of the Site, without notice, for any conduct that we, in our sole discretion, believe is in violation of any applicable law or is harmful to the interests of another user, Associates, or Papajohns.com.
Customers can choose to opt out of the program at any time and will stop receiving promotional emails about the program. This does not terminate customer's future participation in the program, if at a later date customer reinstates their settings, their status in the program will be restored at that time.



General Conditions

To earn and redeem points, customers must enroll in Papa John's Rewards program. Further, by accepting the rewards points, each customer agrees to release and hold harmless Papa John's, its licensees, affiliates, subsidiaries, merchant partners, advertising and promotion agencies and their respective directors, officers, employees, representatives and agents from any and all liability for any injuries, loss or damage of any kind to person, including death, and property, arising in whole or in part, directly or indirectly, from acceptance, use or misuse of the rewards discounts or participation in any Rewards program related activity. This Program is void where prohibited by law. Papa John's reserves the right, at its sole discretion, to disqualify any individual it finds, in its sole discretion, to be tampering with the entry process or the operation of the Rewards program; to be in violation of the Conditions of Use of the web site, to be acting in violation of the sites Policies and Procedures; or to be acting in a non-sportsmanlike or disruptive manner, or with intent to annoy, abuse, threaten or harass any other person. Any use of robotic, automatic, macro, programmed or like entry methods will void all such entries by such methods. In the event of a dispute as to entries submitted by multiple users having the same e-mail account, the authorized subscriber of the e-mail account used to enter the Rewards program at the actual time of entry will be deemed to be the user and must comply with these rules. Authorized account subscriber is deemed to be the natural person who is assigned an e-mail by an Internet access provider, on line service provider or other organization, which is responsible for assigning e-mail, addresses or the domain associated with the submitted e-mail address. Papa John's International will prosecute any fraudulent activities to the full extent of the law.



Limitations of Liability & Disputes

For detailed information on Papa John's Limitations of Liability & Disputes policies please review the site's Conditions of Use.




 
 
 
 








 











